==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Fish-tackle
<hw>Fish"-tac`kle</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A tackle or
purchase used to raise the flukes of the anchor up to the gunwale. The
block used is called the <xex>fish-block</xex>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Fish-tail</ent>⟦br⟧
